spatialDEG

spatialDEG_test.Rd

spatialDEG to perform differentially expressed gene analysis by leveraging spatial information.

spatialDEG_test(
  spa1,
  spa2,
  W,
  Y,
  Initial_theta,
  num_ls = 20L,
  mu_fixed = TRUE,
  verbose = TRUE
)

Arguments

spa1

spatial location for the first dataset.
spa2

spatial location for the second dataset.
W

covariates for the two datasets
Y

stacked gene expression
Initial_theta

initial value of theta
num_ls

total number of length scale and periodicity
mu_fixed

logical value specifying whether mu is fixed
verbose

logical value specifying whether to print the parameters during the spatialDEG analysis or not

Value

List of model parameters

Details

spatialDEG_test run spatialDEG model.

Author

Yi Yang
